<p>
<note n="0568003" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0568003">〔故〕－【宋】【元】【明】，故＝如【宮】</note>
<note n="0569001" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0569001">雖＝離【宋】【元】【明】</note>
<note n="0569003" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0569003">由＝田【宋】【元】【明】</note>
<note n="0569004" resp="#resp2" type="mod" target="#nkr_note_mod_0569004">繁＝煩【宋】【元】【明】【宮】</note>
